e calmed down from the drama. She watched Var go off and get cookies and watched her come back and set them down. She then watched Deia feed her cookies to the fox,then eat her own. <br>
<br>
She rubs her head,then leans back on the couch,getting as comfortable as possible,while still having Deia sitting on her lap. Reclining one arm on the arm rest and the other arm on the back of the couch.<br>
<br>
She breathed in heavily,then wrinkled her nose at the smell of the cookies. Yuck. Still not use to the smell of human food. Blah.<br>
<br>
She picks Deia up off her lap and sets her down on the other side of the couch as she stands up. &quot;I think i'm going to go have a breath of fresh air.&quot; She managed a smile then walked out of the hut to stand outside.<br>
