<br>
&quot;Greetings Sisters all, &quot; The woman aclaimed them as she approached, &quot; I am Tiya for those who now me not,!&quot; She smiled and nodded towards the women she had met the day before.<br>
<br>
As she came close, she saw the child and her face lit with the broadest of smiles.<br>
She came right up to the girl and scooped her up, raising her high.  Flashing the child a smile, which she shared with the women there, she excalimed.<br>
<br>
&quot;My you are a pretty one,&quot;  looking around the women, &quot; Isn't she just adorable?  Which of you is her mother?&quot;   Tiya gave the girl a big but gentle hug and carefully placed her back where she had been standing.....<br>
