<br>
Zelia raised an eyebrow when TiYa entered her and Varia's hut to greet them.<br>
<br>
&quot;Hello TiYa.&quot; She walked back into the hut. Looking at TiYa. &quot;That was a good question.&quot; About who Deia's mother was. She looked to Deia then to Varia,then walked past them all and entered the kitchen and got herself a cup of water. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/utiyakuktai.showPublicProfile?language=EN>TiYa KukTai</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.goldenwonders.com/graphics/dragon.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 29<br> <font color=#993300>(9/17/02 3:59 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm40.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=54.topic&index=95>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.goldenwonders.com/graphics/dragon.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: blink blink</span><hr size=1> Tiya smiled at the child's surprise.  Goddess Bia often forgot her strength in human form.<br>
<br>
&quot;Do not fear little one,&quot; she smiled to the child, &quot;you have a goddess to protect you.&quot;  <br>
<br>
She turned when Zelia spoke,  &quot; Yasoo Zelia Mun,&quot; she replied, &quot;I'm sorry, I hadn't seen you when I came in.  I do apologise&quot;.  Tiya flashed a smle which could have blinded an army..   She spoke in Zelia's mind  &quot;Indeed, it is a good question, is it not&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uxdeiamaex.showPublicProfile?language=EN>XDeiaMaeX</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_thatch.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 45<br> <font color=#993300>(9/17/02 8:27 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm40.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=54.topic&index=96>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: blink blink</span><hr size=1> Deia giggled as she was told that she had a goddess to protect her. She looked to Varia innocently. &quot;She say I's gotsa...a..da moon lady's ta watch over's me's,&quot; she meant Artemis, being that she was the only goddess she had ever seen her real mother pray to. She walked over to Varia, feeling a bit too tiny among the three women, partially hiding herself from view behind her. <p>Deianeira Maera~ innocence, power, and grace wrapped up in one tiny body~</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uiizeliaii.showPublicProfile?language=EN>II Zelia II</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Silver Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 221<br> <font color=#993300>(9/18/02 1:54 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm40.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=54.topic&index=97>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> -.-</span><hr size=1> Zelia walked back out to look at TiYa. Her face showed little to no emotions,finding out TiYa was a goddess didn't really please Zelia,nor did it please her for TiYa to mind speak to her.<br>
<br>
&quot;TiYa,why do you cover your true identity? Who are you under your mask?&quot; After she finished her question,she took a drink of her water,then set the cup down on a nearby table. She then crossed her arms over her chest.<br>
<br>
For some strange reason Zelia had suddenly not been able to pick up on whether someone was mortal,immortal,human or whatnot.Infact,her sences seemed dulled. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ugoddessbia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Goddess Bia</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://images.amazon.com/images/P/1560252154.01.LZZZZZZZ.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 19<br> <font color=#993300>(9/18/02 12:17 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm40.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=54.topic&index=98>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://images.amazon.com/images/P/1560252154.01.LZZZZZZZ.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: -.-</span><hr size=1> Tiya decided perhaps Zelia was right in some ways.   Why did she hide herself in human form?<br>
<br>
&quot;Well,&quot; Bia replied,&quot; So you wish to see me as I am?&quot;  <br>
<br>
Bia removed her cloak, the cloak she wore as Tiya that is.  From the tall dark skinned woman there was a flash of black smoke and dazzling golden light.<br>
<br>
The Goddess Bia stood before them.  She towered above the assembly, perhaps reaching well over 100' tall. Only her sister Nike and brothers  Cratos and Zelus equalled her stature among the Gods, for their father was Pallas the Giant and their Mother was Styx the undying one.  Her Dark skin contrasted with the gold of her tunic.   Huge golden wings flexed themselves gracefully while her still dark hair seemed to tumble down her back forever.  She held a golden bow and on her shoulder was a quiver.  Her sword hung about her waist and the Golden Dragon she wore around her neck  snarled and spouted fire.<br>
<br>
Goddess Bia turned to Zelia and in a voice which almost deafened them all (even though in fact she spoke softly) said,&quot; This is why I appear among you all as Tiya.  But know this, I am a friend to Amazons and as Tiya I am a fellow athelfi.  My intention is not to disceive, for I have nothing to hide.  I spare you the shock of the vision which now stands before you.  For I am  Goddess Bia, Goddess of Force and Power,  Warrior among the Gods and Guardian of Zeus.  To you all here, I appear as Tiya.  Know she is your friend and alley.&quot;  <br>
<br>
All the while she spoke the golden dragon around her neck spouted fire.  Her eyes burned like two suns and the vision of this Golden Warrior Goddess was truely an awesome and terrible shimmering sight of dazzling golden light.<br>
<br>
Once she stopped speaking, again black smoke engulfed those present and a brilliant golden flash, revealed  Tiya, once more standing before them.  She looked at their expressions, variously of fear, surprise, and perhaps discomfort.<br>
<br>
&quot;Now you all know,&quot; she smiled her dazzling smile around the assembled group of athelfi. &quot; I appear to you as Tiya, in respect of you all.  Know that I am your friend.&quot;   Smiling again holding out her arms, &quot; I am your fellow athelfi, do not be alarmed, but be at peace one and all.&quot; she concluded....... the golden dragon about her neck seemed to move and it's eyes sparkled....... <br>
<br>
 <p>~ ~ Bia  Goddess of Force and Power: Warrior and Guardian of Zeus ~ ~

